<title>USA: Franklin sees FY 1997 oper EPS $1.90-$1.95.</title>
<headline>Franklin sees FY 1997 oper EPS $1.90-$1.95.</headline>
<dateline>SALT LAKE CITY, Utah 1997-07-29</dateline>
<text>
<p>Franklin Covey said Tuesday it expects operating results for year-end 1997 to be in the range of $1.90 to $1.95 per share, excluding a one-time write-off related to the merger.</p>
<p>The company said it expects one-time merger costs to be about $5 million.</p>
<p>Projected results translate to an increase in earnings per share of about 15 percent compared to fiscal 1996.&quot;</p>
<p>Franklin Quest Co and Covey Leadership Center completed their merger in May 1997.</p>
